1
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:35,980
♪Looking at the bright lights
of the long streets in my hometown♪

2
00:00:36,260 --> 00:00:39,480
♪I wrote down
that it's not too late to meet you♪

3
00:00:39,780 --> 00:00:45,260
♪Rereading it now,
I think it's just a joke in life♪

4
00:00:46,540 --> 00:00:49,580
♪During my beautiful youth,
I longed for peace♪

5
00:00:49,740 --> 00:00:53,240
♪I vowed to face challenges with you
before Buddha♪

6
00:00:53,940 --> 00:00:59,380
♪I pray to the gods not to be alone♪

7
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:03,140
♪Singing about farewell at Yang Pass♪

8
00:01:03,340 --> 00:01:06,300
♪Behind the sad song,
no one knows how I feel♪

9
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:13,100
♪Even though the streets are bustling,
I can only watch alone♪

10
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:16,500
♪Spend years on the sea,
drifting through foreign lands♪

11
00:01:16,780 --> 00:01:20,580
♪There have been
reunions and separations♪

12
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:26,300
♪There are countless sceneries,
none of them are half as good as you♪

13
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:30,180
♪I asked heaven and earth
where we can share the bright moon♪

14
00:01:30,420 --> 00:01:33,340
♪Looking back,
only the wind understands♪

15
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:39,980
♪Turns out that when love is deep,
right and wrong are forgotten♪

16
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:43,500
♪Let me ask you
how black hair turns white?♪

17
00:01:43,820 --> 00:01:47,180
♪I answer myself,
saying it's been a long separation♪

18
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:53,980
♪In the blink of an eye,
I lost my youthful appearance♪

19
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:04,680
=Cao Xuanxuan's Love Journey=

20
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:07,220
=Episode 3=

21
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:09,720
If the body had been burned
and then sunk into the pond,

22
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:10,890
the skin would have contracted

23
00:02:10,890 --> 00:02:12,320
and wouldn't have swollen so quickly.

24
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,840
So

25
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,800
the body wasn't burned.

26
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:16,560
Exactly.

27
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,440
The scholar's cap found
at the arson site

28
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:22,240
doesn't mean the victim

29
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,840
was there beforehand.

30
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:24,880
Look.

31
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,840
His robe,

32
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,960
shoes, and headscarf are all missing.

33
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:30,320
The killer is clearly trying
to mislead us

34
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,760
by burning these items.

35
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:34,040
I think the most important thing now

36
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:36,480
is to investigate

37
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:37,800
how Fu Miao died.

38
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:40,680
Since he wasn't burned,

39
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:43,840
was he drowned?

40
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,800
No.

41
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,280
I just checked.

42
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:48,220
Although there was water
in his mouth and nose,

43
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:50,200
his lungs only contained
a small amount of water.

44
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,840
He must have been submerged

45
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,320
in the water after death.

46
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,240
So it wasn't by burning

47
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:57,320
or drowning.

48
00:02:58,180 --> 00:03:00,480
I've been well-versed
in "Celebrated Cases of Judge Di."

49
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:03,040
I've never encountered
such a strange case.

50
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:06,000
I've read Agatha, Queen,
and Carr's works.

51
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,480
So I've seen all sorts of strange cases.

52
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,760
No matter how bizarre

53
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:12,080
the killer's tricks are,

54
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:13,840
everything will make sense

55
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,640
once the truth is revealed.

56
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:16,920
We just haven't seen

57
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,640
through it yet.

58
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:20,400
Ms. Xuanxuan,

59
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:22,480
are you talking
about the "The Last Manuscript"?

60
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,040
It is also about solving cases?

61
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:25,980
But why have I never heard of it?

62
00:03:30,980 --> 00:03:32,080
Li Ye is running away.

63
00:03:32,740 --> 00:03:33,300
After him!

64
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:35,040
Why is he running away?

65
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,280
Could he be the killer?

66
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,860
Something is definitely wrong with him.

67
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,320
May I know

68
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,840
if you're Mr. Sun?

69
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,920
You are...

70
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,440
If I may ask,

71
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,960
did Li Ye escape?

72
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,800
Who are you?

73
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,080
I didn't kill anyone.

74
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,160
You better behave.

75
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:15,720
Zijie.

76
00:04:16,960 --> 00:04:17,840
Trying to run, huh?

77
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,160
I haven't ordered your arrest yet,

78
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:22,020
but you ran off by yourself?

79
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:22,640
Why?

80
00:04:23,020 --> 00:04:24,500
Is disguising
as Fox Spirit hard now?

81
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:24,880
Sir,

82
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,620
I didn't kill anyone.

83
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:27,080
I swear.

84
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,180
Enough said.

85
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,460
Now that the killer has been caught,

86
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,120
we can go back to report on the results.

87
00:04:32,180 --> 00:04:32,800
By the way,

88
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,800
I ran into

89
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,360
Li Ye's classmate just now.

90
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,680
I am Li Ye's classmate.

91
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,680
My name is Sun Yi from Lin Village.

92
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:43,480
I heard Magistrate Guo is here
to investigate a case.

93
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:45,020
So I came to report something.

94
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:47,200
What is it?

95
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:50,520
Zhao Qiang, Li Ye, and Fu Miao

96
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:52,500
are the top three students
at the town's academy.

97
00:04:52,540 --> 00:04:54,160
Li Ye ranked last among them.

98
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,960
But the three were very close friends.

99
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:56,840
However,

100
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,360
I've seen Li Ye report Fu Miao

101
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:02,400
to their teacher several times
in secret.

102
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,440
Is that true?

103
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:06,920
What did he report?

104
00:05:08,400 --> 00:05:09,680
He accused him

105
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,620
of being a hypocrite dressed
as a scholar

106
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,240
who violated a widow.

107
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:14,080
A widow?

108
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:17,920
According to Sun Yi,

109
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,360
the matter was dropped

110
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:22,080
because of a lack of evidence.

111
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,600
Regardless of Fu Miao's
personal character,

112
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,960
it's not an excuse
to harm your classmate.

113
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:30,800
No, that's not right.

114
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:32,800
What's not right?

115
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:36,000
Whether it was out
of personal grudge or personal gain,

116
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,560
he had the opportunity

117
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:39,180
and the motive to commit the crime.

118
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,920
On top of that, he tried to escape.

119
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:43,720
There's plenty of evidence pointing
to him as the killer.

120
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:46,320
Then how did Fu Miao disappear?

121
00:05:46,580 --> 00:05:48,320
And what about Zhao Qiang
and that house?

122
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:49,640
How did they vanish?

123
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,400
About that...

124
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,760
I haven't figured out yet.

125
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:02,200
Zhao Qiang disappeared without a trace.

126
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,080
Did you already kill him?

127
00:06:04,280 --> 00:06:04,960
Li Ye,

128
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,840
you better tell the truth

129
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:08,800
and spare yourself
from unnecessary suffering.

130
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,520
Sir,

131
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,440
I really don't know where Zhao is,

132
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:14,160
and I didn't kill anyone.

133
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,720
If you didn't kill anyone,

134
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:16,580
why did you run?

135
00:06:16,580 --> 00:06:17,810
Fox Spirit has started to kill!

136
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:18,640
Sir!

137
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,000
Zhao Qiang?

138
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,600
Don't kill me.

139
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,320
It's him.

140
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,320
It's him!

141
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,560
He killed him!

142
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:33,840
He did it!

143
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,440
It was him!

144
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,560
Don't run!

145
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:42,360
He killed him.

146
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,320
Has he lost his mind?

147
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,580
What happened to Zhao Qiang?

148
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,320
He has gone mad.

149
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,040
What is this situation?

150
00:07:09,700 --> 00:07:12,280
I didn't know the people
of Zhao Village were so superstitious.

151
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:15,960
To think he could actually escape
from the Fox Spirit!

152
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,320
But it seems

153
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,320
he has gone mad.

154
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:23,960
Disappear?

155
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,980
He's gone mad,
but he can still find his way?

156
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:38,720
Keep an eye on Zhao Qiang.

157
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,300
I need to head to Zhao Xiaolin's house.

158
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,520
How long has Xuanxuan been gone?

159
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,760
It's been quite a while.

160
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,560
Why is it dark inside?

161
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,040
Let's go inside.

162
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,640
Xuanxuan, are you here?

163
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:14,800
Xuanxuan.

164
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:16,600
Is that you?

165
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:21,000
Is that Xuanxuan?

166
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:22,200
Why is she not answering?

167
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:23,560
Look! She...

168
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,960
She disappeared.

169
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,800
Xuanxuan.

170
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,800
The window is not opened.

171
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:45,920
Don't you agree?

172
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,200
Something is not right.

173
00:08:48,920 --> 00:08:49,720
That's weird.

174
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,520
I clearly saw her just now.

175
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:55,400
But where did she go?

176
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,600
I've figured out the killer's method.

177
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:02,480
Xuanxuan?

178
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:03,440
I thought...

179
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,560
Weren't you inside just now?

180
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:05,840
It's all

181
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,040
an illusion,

182
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,080
which is

183
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,520
what we call magic in our time.

184
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,560
What magic?

185
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:16,520
In your time, this is called a trick.

186
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,440
A trick?

187
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:23,100
Using tricks to commit murder?

188
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,840
If I can solve this case,

189
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:30,600
my reputation will spread far and wide.

190
00:09:31,420 --> 00:09:33,160
Hurry and tell me how it happened.

191
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,440
You promised me, remember?

192
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,680
And if the case is solved,

193
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,180
just say it was me who solved it.

194
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,000
What's in it for me

195
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,320
if I tell you?

196
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,120
What do you want?

197
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,100
You'll have to do what I say after this.

198
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,440
Cao Xuanxuan,

199
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,920
don't push it.

200
00:10:04,020 --> 00:10:05,500
I'm a county magistrate, you know?

201
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:07,200
How can I obey a woman?

202
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,520
If the case is cracked,

203
00:10:08,740 --> 00:10:10,620
you'll be the one
enjoying fame and fortune.

204
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,220
You have nothing to lose here.

205
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:16,240
Is that so?

206
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:23,600
But

207
00:10:24,260 --> 00:10:26,060
I'll only obey you when no one's around.

208
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,580
If there's someone else present,

209
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:29,100
I must still be the one in charge.

210
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,240
It's a deal, then?

211
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:31,960
Deal.

212
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,240
You'll be mine sooner or later.

213
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,480
Just watch how I deal with you.

214
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:36,400
What did you say?

215
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:40,380
I said you made so much contribution
with your hard work.

216
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,920
The family will be counting on you.

217
00:10:45,060 --> 00:10:45,880
All right, then.

218
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,260
I'll tell you how it happened.

219
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:48,920
Follow me.

220
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,680
The shadow you saw

221
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,400
was that thing.

222
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:07,400
It's pretty simple.

223
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:10,480
The killer used a thin string
to control the puppet that night.

224
00:11:10,540 --> 00:11:12,040
It was dark in here at that time.

225
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:13,640
After Zhao Xiaolin entered the house,

226
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:15,320
she thought the puppet was Fu Miao.

227
00:11:15,420 --> 00:11:16,960
During the time it took to light a lamp,

228
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:19,520
the killer pulled the puppet
to the ceiling.

229
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,240
That's why

230
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:23,080
Zhao Xiaolin thought Fu Miao

231
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,520
had disappeared into thin air.

232
00:11:24,940 --> 00:11:26,480
I didn't know such a method existed.

233
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:27,600
Incredible!

234
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:30,640
On the night of the incident,

235
00:11:30,640 --> 00:11:32,480
Zhao Qiang went to town
to buy ink and brush.

236
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,680
Li Ye was the only one here.

237
00:11:35,420 --> 00:11:36,840
Then it really must have been him.

238
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,540
Behave yourself.

239
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,120
Sir, look.

240
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,880
(Arsenic)
I found this on him.

241
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,240
Arsenic?

242
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:48,720
Is this yours?

243
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:53,480
Tell the truth.

244
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,560
I did want

245
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:56,920
to kill Fu Miao.

246
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,400
But he already died

247
00:11:58,420 --> 00:11:59,620
before I made my move.

248
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:00,800
It wasn't me who killed him.

249
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:01,920
We have solid evidence.

250
00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:03,060
Why are you still denying it?

251
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,200
Why did you kill Fu Miao?

252
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,080
Did you come up

253
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:08,480
with the puppet trick yourself,

254
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:09,740
or did someone teach you?

255
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,240
What puppet?

256
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:13,640
I don't know what you mean.

257
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:16,080
I wanted to kill Fu Miao

258
00:12:16,140 --> 00:12:17,900
because he was a wolf
in sheep's clothing!

259
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,200
Explain it.

260
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,240
My childhood sweetheart,

261
00:12:21,380 --> 00:12:22,680
Zhang Qin, had been married

262
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:24,240
to the Zhao Village for a few years

263
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:25,720
before becoming a widow.

264
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:27,440
She is already a woman of misfortune,

265
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:29,080
who lives alone

266
00:12:29,180 --> 00:12:30,760
raising a mentally disabled child.

267
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:31,920
That day,

268
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,840
Fu Miao saw her alone at home.

269
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,840
Driven by lust,

270
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,560
he violated her.

271
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:40,520
Zhang Qin?

272
00:12:40,540 --> 00:12:41,660
It's Madam Zhang.

273
00:12:41,660 --> 00:12:42,990
The one we ran into the other day.

274
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:47,640
So it was a crime passion.

275
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:48,920
No, it wasn't.

276
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:50,960
I ran

277
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,000
because you suspected me

278
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,080
that day.

279
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:56,840
He can't be trusted.

280
00:12:57,280 --> 00:12:58,320
Go and check on Zhang Qin.

281
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:00,440
- All right.
- Yes, sir.

282
00:13:14,920 --> 00:13:15,560
