287
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,080
We are here to ask about Li Ye.

288
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:35,640
Sir,

289
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,600
I don't really know

290
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,200
Li Ye.

291
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:41,000
But I heard

292
