you were childhood sweethearts.

293
00:13:44,140 --> 00:13:45,240
He was spouting nonsense.

294
00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:46,540
Then what about Fu Miao?

295
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:49,120
Don't be afraid.

296
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:50,940
You only need to tell us the truth.

297
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,320
We'll seek justice for you.

298
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,360
Did Fu Miao

299
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,480
violate you?

300
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:02,760
No.

301
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:04,080
