326
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,720
You're not being rational.

327
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:09,160
I can't believe Li Ye managed to escape.

328
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,680
It looks like he is the killer.

329
00:15:11,140 --> 00:15:11,740
How about this?

330
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:12,720
Go and investigate him.

331
00:15:12,740 --> 00:15:13,220
All right.

332
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:14,340
What's the matter?

333
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:15,800
Li Ye escaped.

334
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,400
What?

335
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:19,560
Sir,

336
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:21,760
Xiaohua is missing.

337
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:22,520
Sir.

338
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:23,760
