355
00:15:54,535 --> 00:15:56,375
So I cut off all contact with him.

356
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:58,600
I didn't expect him to come
to the Zhao Village again.

357
00:15:58,720 --> 00:15:59,640
Li Ye is unbelievable.

358
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:01,340
No wonder he escaped.

359
00:16:01,560 --> 00:16:02,760
He's a scholar.

360
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:04,240
Yet, he is so heartless.

361
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:05,640
Li Ye has escaped?

362
00:16:05,920 --> 00:16:07,320
