363
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,760
Calm down.

364
00:16:08,800 --> 00:16:09,920
We'll go and search for her.

365
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,580
Given the situation,

366
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:12,980
