388
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,140
Her name is Xiaohua.

389
00:16:37,180 --> 00:16:37,700
No.

390
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:40,560
Have you seen

391
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:41,560
a girl this tall?

