399
00:16:50,060 --> 00:16:51,400
Thank you for the information.

400
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:52,280
You're welcome.

401
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:54,440
It looks like it was Li Ye

402
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:55,840
who took Xiaohua away.

403
00:16:57,340 --> 00:16:58,820
