441
00:18:35,320 --> 00:18:36,200
I've heard

442
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:38,400
something interesting.

443
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:41,480
The midwife who delivered
the Cao sisters said

444
00:18:42,600 --> 00:18:44,040
Cao Xuanxuan's older sister

445
00:18:44,280 --> 00:18:46,560
had a crescent-shaped birthmark
on her back.

446
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:48,880
A crescent-shaped birthmark?

447
00:18:56,840 --> 00:18:58,560
(This child is badly injured.)

448
00:18:58,800 --> 00:19:00,360
(Her life isn't in danger)

449
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:01,880
(but it'll be a while)

450
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:03,160
(before she wakes up.)

451
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:08,360
Madam Zhang,

452
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:09,560
are you home?

453
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:11,800
Madam Zhang.

454
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:15,920
Madam Zhang.

455
00:19:19,440 --> 00:19:20,080
Madam Zhang.

456
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:21,360
Why are you here again?

457
00:19:21,360 --> 00:19:22,600
You call yourselves officials

458
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:24,480
but you still couldn't catch the killer.

459
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:25,360
We...

460
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:26,880
We're here to catch the killer.

461
00:19:27,280 --> 00:19:28,680
I heard a man came

462
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:29,680
to your house last night.

463
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:30,540
Was that Li Ye?

464
00:19:30,560 --> 00:19:31,680
Why do you like

465
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:33,480
to pick on a widow
and her orphaned child?

466
00:19:33,760 --> 00:19:35,960
Xiaohua is already in such a state.

467
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,120
Don't ever come again!

468
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:40,520
- Madam Zhang!
- Madam Zhang!

469
00:19:52,840 --> 00:19:53,960
It's a man's shoe.

470
00:19:54,620 --> 00:19:56,040
It looks like it belongs to Li Ye.

471
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,240
Are you sure?

472
00:19:59,120 --> 00:19:59,680
Yes.

473
00:20:01,840 --> 00:20:03,400
Go and inform Magistrate Guo first.

474
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,460
I'll go after Li Ye.

475
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:04,440
What is this place?

476
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,040
Why are we here?

477
00:22:06,360 --> 00:22:07,120
The killer

478
00:22:07,340 --> 00:22:08,480
should be executed.

479
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:09,620
I told you

480
00:22:09,660 --> 00:22:10,820
I didn't kill anyone.

481
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:13,140
The child is innocent
and the law shows no mercy.

482
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,140
What child?

483
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:16,240
You still won't admit it, huh?

484
00:22:16,840 --> 00:22:18,200
I may have persuaded

485
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:20,520
