to someone else.

486
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:25,320
But I wouldn't go so far
as to harm a child.

487
00:22:25,760 --> 00:22:27,000
If you didn't try to kill her,

488
00:22:27,040 --> 00:22:29,240
