at the Zhang family's house?

489
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:30,600
What are you saying?

490
00:22:31,320 --> 00:22:32,440
My shoe...

491
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:38,400
Where did your shoe go?

492
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:39,520
Don't tell me you forgot.

493
00:22:40,160 --> 00:22:41,360
My shoes were supposed to be...

494
00:22:42,600 --> 00:22:43,960
Who picked on you?

495
00:22:45,600 --> 00:22:46,880
Your classmate.

496
00:22:47,840 --> 00:22:48,440
Miss He,

497
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,360
let me explain.

498
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:51,200
My classmate is Zhao.

499
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:51,960
You...

500
00:22:53,520 --> 00:22:54,120
Miss He,

501
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:55,160
what are you doing?

502
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,680
I pretended to get caught

503
00:22:57,760 --> 00:22:59,080
to hear the truth from you.

504
00:22:59,560 --> 00:23:00,240
Miss He,

505
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:02,260
everything is a misunderstanding.

506
00:23:02,260 --> 00:23:03,340
You don't have to explain.

507
00:23:03,360 --> 00:23:04,040
Go back

508
00:23:04,040 --> 00:23:05,480
and tell Magistrate Guo everything.

509
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:07,840
Miss He,

510
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:09,600
I'll go with you.

511
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:16,120
Let's go.

512
00:23:26,160 --> 00:23:27,200
What are you thinking?

513
00:23:27,360 --> 00:23:29,080
After He Chun brought Li Ye back here,

514
00:23:29,120 --> 00:23:30,680
won't we get to the bottom of the case?

515
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:32,880
I still have a few doubts.

516
00:23:33,760 --> 00:23:35,960
I still couldn't figure out

517
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:37,820
how Xiaohua and Zhao Qiang disappeared.

518
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:41,080
If you put it that way,

519
00:23:41,840 --> 00:23:44,160
