and the house's disappearance

520
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:45,400
is really strange.

521
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:47,240
Every strange thing

522
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:48,680
can be explained in the end.

523
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:49,920
Maybe

524
00:23:49,960 --> 00:23:51,400
