574
00:26:02,200 --> 00:26:04,280
it just looked like he entered a house.

575
00:26:06,200 --> 00:26:06,960
That's not right.

576
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:08,120
Think about it.

577
00:26:08,440 --> 00:26:09,680
But Zhao Qiang went in himself.

578
00:26:09,680 --> 00:26:11,520
Couldn't he tell it was just a wall?

579
00:26:17,800 --> 00:26:20,000
Are you saying Zhao Qiang
is behind everything?

580
00:26:20,320 --> 00:26:20,960
Exactly.

581
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:24,320
But what is his motive?

582
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:26,960
At the time,
only Fu Miao had disappeared.

583
00:26:27,640 --> 00:26:28,760
So you're saying

584
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,520
Li Ye isn't the killer

585
00:26:30,840 --> 00:26:31,600
but it was

586
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:32,800
Zhao Qiang's doing?

587
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:34,520
It's possible.

588
00:26:35,840 --> 00:26:36,640
But

589
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:38,560
I'm more curious

590
00:26:38,760 --> 00:26:40,560
about how he came up with this idea

591
00:26:40,800 --> 00:26:42,000
and pulled it off.

592
00:26:42,320 --> 00:26:44,040
Who cares how he did it?

593
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:45,760
Just catch the killer will do!

594
00:26:46,080 --> 00:26:47,040
You wouldn't understand.

595
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:50,360
Why wouldn't I understand?

596
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:51,840
Xuanxuan.

597
00:26:52,280 --> 00:26:52,920
Zijie.

598
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:54,340
I just want to check on her.

599
00:26:54,840 --> 00:26:55,880
Be rational.

600
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:02,000
Where are you going?

601
00:27:02,540 --> 00:27:03,680
It's already dark outside.

602
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:04,820
How about going back inside?

603
00:27:04,860 --> 00:27:06,100
I want to be alone.

604
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:07,040
So let me be.

605
00:27:39,380 --> 00:27:42,780
♪Looking at the bright lights
of the long streets in my hometown♪

606
00:27:42,820 --> 00:27:45,980
♪I wrote down
that it's not too late to meet you♪

607
00:27:47,160 --> 00:27:48,840
Tomorrow is already the deadline.

608
00:27:50,320 --> 00:27:51,400
He Chun is not back yet.

609
00:27:52,520 --> 00:27:53,720
Why are you suddenly

610
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:56,000
so eager to solve this case?

611
00:27:56,360 --> 00:27:57,480
And what about you?

612
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:59,040
Are you worried

613
00:27:59,320 --> 00:28:00,440
about your position?

614
00:28:01,040 --> 00:28:02,320
I'm worried

615
00:28:02,320 --> 00:28:03,520
if I lose my post,

616
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:05,480
your life as my child bride

617
00:28:05,840 --> 00:28:07,120
will only get harder.

618
00:28:07,120 --> 00:28:09,720
♪Singing about farewell at Yang Pass♪

619
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:12,160
♪Behind the sad song,
no one knows how I feel♪

620
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:13,760
You know, sometimes

621
00:28:14,280 --> 00:28:15,840
I think staying here isn't so bad.

622
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:17,600
Where will you go

623
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,920
if you don't stay here?

624
00:28:19,040 --> 00:28:20,100
Return to Cao Manor?

625
00:28:20,920 --> 00:28:21,800
You won't understand.

626
00:28:25,080 --> 00:28:26,480
If I can crack

627
00:28:26,760 --> 00:28:28,280
this case,

628
00:28:29,120 --> 00:28:30,720
it'll give me new content

629
00:28:31,040 --> 00:28:32,480
for my masterpiece!

630
00:28:34,600 --> 00:28:35,880
Future generations will marvel

631
00:28:36,120 --> 00:28:38,680
at my brilliance and heroism.

632
00:28:41,220 --> 00:28:42,460
So, how's that book of yours

633
00:28:42,500 --> 00:28:43,340
coming along?

634
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:44,860
Are you curious?

635
00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:46,280
I'm not telling you.

636
00:28:46,600 --> 00:28:47,660
Are you coming or not?

637
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,040
If you don't, I am leaving.

638
00:28:50,280 --> 00:28:50,920
I'm leaving now.

639
00:28:53,900 --> 00:29:00,140
♪In the blink of an eye,
I lost my youthful appearance♪

640
00:29:03,680 --> 00:29:03,960
Here.

641
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:07,600
Watch the steps.

642
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,000
We're about to leave

643
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,740
this small interrogation room of yours.

644
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:22,720
I really do feel a bit attached to it.

645
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:25,920
Actually,

646
00:29:26,240 --> 00:29:27,800
I kind of regret it.

647
00:29:28,560 --> 00:29:30,240
I shouldn't have made such bold claims.

648
00:29:30,600 --> 00:29:31,640
It's not your fault.

649
00:29:32,280 --> 00:29:33,320
Even without you,

650
00:29:33,520 --> 00:29:34,640
Imperial Envoy could still

651
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:36,480
accuse me
of being all talk and no action.

652
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:38,200
You let me keep
my position for a few days.

653
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:44,600
Sir.

654
00:29:45,760 --> 00:29:47,160
Li Ye, you rascal.

655
00:29:47,560 --> 00:29:48,620
I might just drag you back

656
00:29:48,620 --> 00:29:50,440
to the administrative office
and sentence you.

657
00:29:50,440 --> 00:29:51,500
Li Ye is not the killer.

658
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:52,200
Li Ye,

659
00:29:52,280 --> 00:29:52,880
tell them now.

660
00:29:53,320 --> 00:29:53,760
Sir,

661
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,760
Qin told me

662
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:57,120
the one who bullied her

663
00:29:57,120 --> 00:29:58,120
was my classmate.

664
00:29:58,680 --> 00:29:59,920
I've always thought it was Fu.

665
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:02,120
But I didn't expect it

666
00:30:02,520 --> 00:30:03,320
to be Zhao.

667
00:30:04,440 --> 00:30:05,080
That day,

668
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:06,440
it was Zhao

669
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:07,920
who helped me escape.

670
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:12,520
Zhao.

671
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:13,520
Li.

672
00:30:13,840 --> 00:30:14,920
What are you doing here?

673
00:30:18,760 --> 00:30:19,760
I trust

674
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:20,960
your character.

675
00:30:21,740 --> 00:30:24,460
But that useless official bragged
in front of the Imperial Envoy

676
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:26,300
that he would solve the case
in five days.

677
00:30:26,560 --> 00:30:27,800
Now that time's running out,

678
00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:29,160
he might pin the blame on you

679
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,340
to save himself.

680
00:30:31,080 --> 00:30:31,880
Zhao,

681
00:30:32,200 --> 00:30:32,640
what

682
00:30:33,280 --> 00:30:34,480
do I do now?

683
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:35,920
The only option

684
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:38,280
is to run for it.

685
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:41,320
All right.

686
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:43,680
Let me help.

687
00:30:45,600 --> 00:30:46,120
Li,

688
00:30:46,920 --> 00:30:48,080
you should leave here for now.

689
00:30:49,220 --> 00:30:51,280
My father is acquainted
with the prefect.

690
00:30:51,600 --> 00:30:52,480
When I go back home,

691
00:30:52,560 --> 00:30:53,880
I'll have my father send a letter

692
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:55,480
to clear your name.

693
00:30:56,320 --> 00:30:56,960
All right.

694
00:30:59,120 --> 00:30:59,800
Leave now.

695
00:31:00,200 --> 00:31:00,920
Zhao,

696
00:31:02,320 --> 00:31:03,240
I'll never forget

697
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:04,520
this kindness.

698
00:31:04,520 --> 00:31:05,080
Say no more.

699
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:05,640
Leave now.

700
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:06,340
All right.

701
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,020
It's too late for that.

702
00:31:11,600 --> 00:31:12,120
Hurry.

703
00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:12,640
All right.

704
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:14,560
Sir,

705
00:31:15,080 --> 00:31:16,640
Li Ye is telling the truth.

706
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:19,160
He and I have a past.

707
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:20,600
He thought

708
00:31:20,800 --> 00:31:22,480
Fu Miao violated me

709
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:25,240
so he tried to poison him with arsenic.

710
00:31:25,520 --> 00:31:26,480
But in the end,

711
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:29,040
it turned out to be Zhao Qiang.

712
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:30,160
Even so,

713
00:31:31,200 --> 00:31:31,880
that is just

714
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:33,200
your side of the story.

715
00:31:35,360 --> 00:31:37,360
Unless we figure out
Zhao Qiang's tricks,

716
00:31:38,120 --> 00:31:40,160
we can't get solid evidence.

717
00:31:42,480 --> 00:31:43,640
The trial is tomorrow.

718
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:45,040
Let's see what happens.

719
00:32:05,980 --> 00:32:07,460
What are you thinking about?

720
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,600
I have one too.

721
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:16,320
I have more or less figured it out.

722
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:18,280
There's only one more thing to do.

723
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:19,680
Let's go.

724
00:32:23,280 --> 00:32:24,440
Take care, Young Master.

725
00:32:24,840 --> 00:32:25,400
All right.

726
00:32:25,520 --> 00:32:26,640
Everyone will be rewarded.

727
00:32:29,060 --> 00:32:29,680
Young Master.

728
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:30,440
Mister, be careful.

729
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:31,020
Young Master.

730
00:32:31,060 --> 00:32:31,640
Who are you?

731
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:32,560
Everything is done.

732
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:33,720
What is it?

733
00:32:37,560 --> 00:32:38,000
Never mind.

734
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:38,840
I get it.

735
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,040
Go and get your reward.

736
00:32:40,140 --> 00:32:41,160
Thank you, Young Master.

737
00:32:42,780 --> 00:32:45,940
(Yan Administrative Office)

738
00:32:49,520 --> 00:32:50,360
Bring in the suspect!

739
00:32:53,660 --> 00:32:57,240
(Impartial and Upright)

740
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:57,680
Sir,

741
00:32:58,280 --> 00:32:59,500
what's the meaning of this?

742
00:32:59,760 --> 00:33:00,480
Didn't you say

743
00:33:00,600 --> 00:33:01,560
Li Ye is the killer?

744
00:33:01,700 --> 00:33:02,960
Why are you arresting me?

745
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:05,160
Zhao Qiang,

746
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:06,400
how dare you lie?

747
00:33:07,660 --> 00:33:09,560
Zhao Qiang,
you killed your classmate, Fu Miao,

748
00:33:09,560 --> 00:33:11,410
while pretending
it was the work of Fox Spirit.

749
00:33:11,520 --> 00:33:12,520
Are you still denying it

750
00:33:13,100 --> 00:33:14,540
when it has escalated to this point?

751
00:33:14,840 --> 00:33:15,520
On your knees!

752
00:33:17,840 --> 00:33:18,440
Sir,

753
00:33:18,760 --> 00:33:19,800
what do you mean by this?

754
00:33:20,320 --> 00:33:21,480
The day Fu disappeared,

755
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:23,560
I was in town buying ink and brush.

756
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:26,760
How could I have killed him
when I was over ten li away?

757
00:33:26,820 --> 00:33:28,020
Buying ink and brush, huh?

758
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:29,640
Fine.

759
00:33:30,600 --> 00:33:31,320
Summon Li Ye.

760
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:33,360
Summon

761
00:33:33,560 --> 00:33:34,920
witness, Li Ye to the court!

762
00:33:37,480 --> 00:33:38,000
Sir.

763
00:33:38,000 --> 00:33:38,680
Li,

764
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:39,600
perfect timing.

765
00:33:39,960 --> 00:33:40,960
Tell the magistrate

766
00:33:41,010 --> 00:33:42,540
that I was in town buying ink and brush

767
00:33:42,560 --> 00:33:43,500
the day Fu went missing.

768
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:43,870
You...

769
00:33:43,880 --> 00:33:45,040
You murderer!

770
00:33:45,560 --> 00:33:46,720
You got me into this mess

771
00:33:46,780 --> 00:33:48,420
and now you want me to be your alibi?

772
00:33:50,320 --> 00:33:51,000
I, Li Ye,

773
00:33:51,040 --> 00:33:51,900
at your service, sir.

774
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:53,720
I want you to answer truthfully

775
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:55,440
the questions I'm going to ask.

776
00:33:56,120 --> 00:33:57,000
I swear

777
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:58,520
to tell you everything I know.

778
00:33:59,120 --> 00:34:00,400
Bring the evidence forward!

779
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,080
Li Ye, look at this.

780
00:34:06,500 --> 00:34:08,040
Is this the set of ink and brush

781
00:34:08,560 --> 00:34:09,920
Zhao Qiang bought that day?

782
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:10,840
Yes.

783
00:34:21,640 --> 00:34:22,160
Sir,

784
00:34:22,720 --> 00:34:24,000
I'm certain this is the one.

785
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:25,120
Zhao Qiang,

786
00:34:26,200 --> 00:34:27,440
come and take a look.

787
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:30,200
Is this what you bought?

788
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:35,520
Sir,

789
00:34:35,660 --> 00:34:37,080
this is exactly what I bought.

790
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:38,640
This proves

791
00:34:38,880 --> 00:34:39,800
I wasn't

792
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:41,120
in Zhao Village that day.

793
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:42,880
So, are you admitting you're a fool?

794
00:34:43,480 --> 00:34:44,560
Why do you say that?

795
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:46,440
That's right.

796
00:34:47,200 --> 00:34:48,000
Magistrate Guo,

797
00:34:48,240 --> 00:34:49,440
why did you say that?

798
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:51,360
Are you messing with me

799
00:34:51,600 --> 00:34:52,720
just to solve the case?

800
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:54,040
Sir, calm down.

801
00:34:55,600 --> 00:34:57,520
Summon Mr. Qian Mai

802
00:34:57,520 --> 00:34:58,760
to the court.

803
00:35:02,680 --> 00:35:03,320
Master,

804
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:04,960
they've caught the killer.

805
00:35:05,640 --> 00:35:06,840
It's Zhao Qiang.

806
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:09,440
Young Master Zijie
is still questioning him.

807
00:35:11,080 --> 00:35:13,440
I've heard good things

808
00:35:14,440 --> 00:35:16,080
about this Zhao kid.

809
00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:18,360
Could Zijie

810
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:19,760
have made a mistake?

811
00:35:20,480 --> 00:35:21,960
It shouldn't be.

812
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:23,480
This won't do.

813
00:35:23,680 --> 00:35:24,880
I don't feel easy about this.

814
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:26,000
I need to go and take a look.

815
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:29,960
Master.

816
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:31,360
Master,

817
00:35:31,880 --> 00:35:33,200
why don't you rest?

818
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:34,960
It's a huge case.

819
00:35:35,640 --> 00:35:36,760
Young Master Zijie will know

820
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:38,640
what to do.

821
00:35:41,200 --> 00:35:42,000
Go

822
00:35:42,560 --> 00:35:44,480
and bring Zilu here now.

823
00:35:45,200 --> 00:35:45,920
Yes, Master.

824
00:35:51,240 --> 00:35:52,360
I, Qian Mai,

825
00:35:52,680 --> 00:35:54,000
greet Magistrate Guo.

826
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:55,040
Qian Mai,

827
00:35:56,600 --> 00:35:57,960
this ink and brush set

828
00:35:58,360 --> 00:35:59,760
has your shop's label.

829
00:36:00,320 --> 00:36:01,000
Take a look

830
00:36:01,260 --> 00:36:02,720
and see if Zhao Qiang bought this

831
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:03,640
from your store

832
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:05,000
on the eighth of this month.

833
00:36:05,240 --> 00:36:06,040
Yes, sir.

834
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:09,120
This is indeed from my shop.

835
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:10,440
Mr. Zhao did come

836
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:12,080
to my store this month

837
00:36:12,080 --> 00:36:13,140
to buy ink and brushes.

838
00:36:13,200 --> 00:36:14,120
But

839
00:36:15,680 --> 00:36:17,720
it was on the seventh, not the eighth.

840
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,280
You're lying!

841
00:36:21,120 --> 00:36:21,720
Sir,

842
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:23,200
don't believe what he said.

843
00:36:23,320 --> 00:36:24,320
But I clearly bought it

844
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:25,800
on the eighth!

845
00:36:26,160 --> 00:36:26,720
Sir,

846
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:28,160
I dare not lie.

847
00:36:28,520 --> 00:36:29,960
I clearly remember

848
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:32,920
this type of brush was sold out
on the eighth.

849
00:36:33,160 --> 00:36:34,720
And Mr. Zhao bought

850
00:36:34,720 --> 00:36:36,800
the last brush on the seventh.

851
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:38,240
Zhao Qiang.

852
00:36:38,440 --> 00:36:39,680
So, where were you

853
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:42,200
on the eighth?

854
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:43,160
Sir,

855
00:36:44,040 --> 00:36:44,880
maybe

856
00:36:45,240 --> 00:36:46,840
I've mistaken the day.

857
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:47,480
But

858
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:49,160
this doesn't prove

859
00:36:49,720 --> 00:36:51,200
that I killed Fu.

860
00:36:52,360 --> 00:36:52,920
Ah, yes.

861
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:55,320
It's clearly the work of the demon fox.

862
00:36:55,520 --> 00:36:57,400
That day, I was captured
by the demon fox!

863
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:01,120
Cao Xuanxuan.

864
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:02,480
Present.

865
00:37:07,020 --> 00:37:09,140
There's no such thing
as a demon fox causing trouble

866
00:37:09,140 --> 00:37:10,300
or disappearing into thin air.

867
00:37:10,340 --> 00:37:11,640
It's all just magic tricks.

868
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,440
What magic?

869
00:37:12,720 --> 00:37:13,520
A trick

870
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:14,700
that misleads people.

871
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:17,320
That day, Zhao Qiang pretended

872
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:20,080
to go and buy ink and brushes

873
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:22,720
but snuck into his house instead.

874
00:37:23,160 --> 00:37:24,880
I'm only worried about you.

875
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:26,000
I told you

876
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:28,180
messing with the Fox Spirit
will bring big trouble.

877
00:37:28,200 --> 00:37:29,880
What's wrong with me eating
some fox meat?

878
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:31,040
If I want to eat it, I will!

879
00:37:31,040 --> 00:37:32,100
It doesn't concern you.

880
00:37:32,140 --> 00:37:33,260
Fine, then I won't bother.

881
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,040
Just leave.

882
00:37:42,160 --> 00:37:42,600
Zhao,

883
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:43,600
Zhao, you're back.

884
00:37:43,620 --> 00:37:44,080
Fu,

885
00:37:44,240 --> 00:37:45,240
come with me quickly.

886
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:46,380
I have something urgent.

887
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:46,960
All right.

888
00:37:49,240 --> 00:37:49,800
Zhao.

889
00:37:51,120 --> 00:37:51,680
Zhao.

890
00:37:52,340 --> 00:37:54,740
Why are you bringing me out here
in the middle of the night?

891
00:37:55,440 --> 00:37:56,080
Fu,

892
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:58,040
this isn't the place to talk.

893
00:37:58,480 --> 00:37:59,760
Let's go somewhere quieter.

894
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:51,280
Miao.

895
00:38:51,960 --> 00:38:52,800
Miao!

896
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:01,920
Sir,

897
00:39:02,440 --> 00:39:03,240
this is how

898
00:39:03,400 --> 00:39:04,640
the disappearance happened.

899
00:39:05,680 --> 00:39:07,300
I didn't know such a thing was possible.

900
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:09,960
I've never heard of such a thing.

901
00:39:10,080 --> 00:39:10,680
Sir,

902
00:39:11,760 --> 00:39:12,880
she's making it all up!

903
00:39:13,200 --> 00:39:14,200
She doesn't have proof.

904
00:39:14,560 --> 00:39:15,560
It means nothing!

905
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,440
The proof

906
00:39:16,840 --> 00:39:18,160
is the missing house itself.

907
00:39:49,761 --> 00:39:55,641
♪Like the setting sun,
which repeatedly sets in the west♪

908
00:39:56,901 --> 00:40:02,341
♪My heart goes over mountains
to rest with you♪

909
00:40:03,501 --> 00:40:06,941
♪As the winds and clouds shift,
our encounter♪

910
00:40:06,941 --> 00:40:10,701
♪Seems like the perfect foreshadowing♪

911
00:40:11,101 --> 00:40:16,141
♪But it was a misplaced expectation♪

912
00:40:17,661 --> 00:40:20,741
♪I think I'm exceptionally affectionate♪

913
00:40:20,941 --> 00:40:23,861
♪Devotion can warm the coldest ice♪

914
00:40:24,221 --> 00:40:27,421
♪And you're a shooting star
that flashes by♪

915
00:40:27,861 --> 00:40:30,141
♪Out of reach♪

916
00:40:31,221 --> 00:40:34,421
♪I prayed for a miracle countless times♪

917
00:40:34,701 --> 00:40:38,821
♪If I meet you, I only wish
we could be together forever♪

918
00:40:39,101 --> 00:40:45,221
♪But only the distant phantom remains♪

919
00:40:45,341 --> 00:40:48,381
♪Love rises like the wind
but remains unsettled when it stops♪

920
00:40:48,661 --> 00:40:51,661
♪Chasing you through four seasons,
wandering for a lifetime♪

921
00:40:51,941 --> 00:40:53,621
♪Fish in the water♪

922
00:40:53,621 --> 00:40:58,861
♪Is greedy for the reflection
of clouds in the heart of the lake♪

923
00:40:59,061 --> 00:41:01,981
♪From dusk to dawn,
from heavy snow to early clear sky♪

924
00:41:02,181 --> 00:41:06,501
♪Searching for your footprints
from south to west♪

925
00:41:06,861 --> 00:41:12,501
♪The wind stops,
but the dream isn't over♪
